MARKET TRENDS:

Analyzing the Upward Trajectory

of Tech Stocks

The tech sector continues to soar as we enter the second quarter of 2025. Major players like Apple, Amazon, and Microsoft have reported record-breaking profits, driving the NASDAQ to new heights. Analysts attribute this growth to increased demand for digital services and innovative technologies amidst a rapidly evolving global landscape.
